entries.femaleVariant: Have you ever experienced anything that changed the meaning of existence? Changed your life?
Yes.
No.
Don't feel like talking about it.
Can't correct murder.
Uh, any reason you're telling me this?
A tale of repentance and rebirth? Gimme a break…
Can't say I have, no.
Could say that, sure.
Don't feel like talkin' about it.
Twelve years ago I was sentenced to prison for armed robbery.
Then you will understand exactly what I'm trying to do.
Too bad. We should all have a moment like that. I've had mine.
Hm. Then let me speak.
And other sins. I shot and killed several people in cold blood, and it didn't mean anything to me at the time.
But behind bars, you get all the time in the world to think. And I thought to correct the errors of my ways.
Still don't get why you're tellin' me this.
entries.maleVariant: I still don't get why you're tellin' me this.

entries.femaleVariant: Spelling mistakes you can correct. But murder's murder.
entries.maleVariant: Spelling mistakes you can correct. But murder is murder.

entries.femaleVariant: A tale of repentance, redemption and rebirth? Been on TV thousands of times, probably. I'm usually asleep before it's half over.
Why'd you shoot 'em?
Why'd you shoot 'em?
I was holding a gun. I didn't like the way they looked at me, and I had the power to stop them.
I still see their faces just before I... Ahem. Frozen in time. God... give me strength to never forget.
You can make amends to the families…
I want you to understand what I am about to do.
This won't be TV. This will be entirely different.
Spill already. What do you want from me?
Stay with me for the day. And I'll pay you what you were promised to kill me.
Uh, excuse me – with what money?
Not mine. The studio's. And the studio will pay.
Not likin' this one bit. Lemme out, I'll be on my way.
Sure, why not.
Drop me off at the next corner, will ya?
Just till the end of the day?
Still got no idea what it is you want from me.
entries.maleVariant: I still got no idea what it is you want from me.

entries.femaleVariant: Still have no idea what you want me to do.
We're almost at Gloria El-Ahmar's.
Till the end of the day.
No one will force you to stay.
It's easy money. Just, uh... give it a thought.
Remain by my side and talk to me. That's it.
I sense anything goin' wrong, I'm out.
Just wish I could've talked to Gloria, explained everything…
If somehow I thought... I-I thought she'd find it in her heart to forgive me…
Give me a moment, I need to prepare.
Fuck, here we go...
Fuck... the hell possessed me to get in…
You can lead others away from the path of darkness.
You know, still got that contract to kill you. What's to stop me from fulfilling?
Me. One strange twitch, I kill you.
Hey, there's no reason to upset Vasquez. Your fixer will get what they want. I'll make sure of it.
How you figure that?
Trust me. Everyone will be satisfied. I guarantee it.
Can't talk to Rachel?
Could try taming Vasquez.
Are you lonely?
You don't like Rachel? She's got the gift of the gab, surely.
entries.maleVariant: Don't like Rachel? She's got the gift of the gab, surely.

entries.femaleVariant: Try Vasquez. You can probably get him to speak if you dangle a dog treat in front of his nose.
Why? Are you lonely?
I'm merely a springboard for her career. Heh, a high-value asset.
You're the one I want to talk to.
Go fuck yourself.
Vasquez sees me as nothing but a liar, scum that should've fried in the electric chair.
You're the one I want to talk to.
Yes, I am.
I truly need you.
Still on contract to kill you.
Who can blame her?
Huh, time to grab a bite to eat.
Who could blame her? Not easy to forgive your son's murderer.
entries.maleVariant: Who can blame her? It's not easy to forgive your son's murderer.

entries.femaleVariant: Hey, probably would've forgiven you if that had been me.
Gloria should have forgiven you.
Where we gonna eat?
Where're we eatin'?
Uhh, PieZ.
They do a great cup of coffee.
Stephenson, we all knew how that would end.
"If you forgive anyone their sins, they are forgiven. If you do not forgive them, they are not forgiven." Pff... ugh.
But you're not her, are you? Nobody killed your son.
Vasquez!
Really gonna submit, let yourself get crucified?
PieZ serves up a killer cheesecake.
Making a braindance of a crucifixion? Really?
You really wanna do this? Get nailed to a cross?
Really aim to spin a virtu of your crucifixion?
entries.maleVariant: You really aim to spin a virtu of your crucifixion?

entries.femaleVariant: Got a killer cheesecake at PieZ…
It is something I must do.
Yes.
Ugh, yes, really.
You'll be kickin' up a shitstorm...
Haters gonna hate.
For if this won't shake the world to its core, and wake us from our collective nightmare, then nothing will.
I'm lactose intolerant.
How 'bout vegan avocado ice cream, then?
Can't ever truly know Night City.
How well do you know the city?
Why's it matter?
Why does it matter?
Ah, just curious. Happen to like it out here is all.
Can't know Night City well, ever. It's always changing... always surprising. Part of its charm.
entries.maleVariant: You can't know Night City well, ever. It's always changin', always surprisin'. Part of its charm.

entries.femaleVariant: Hm, true that.
Ehh, take Stephenson inside, grab us all a table.
Need a word with our stowaway here.
